body:
It is resolved now.
I am not sure the right troubleshoot, but when I restructured my model such a way that it does occupy less space then this issue has not been observed.

Earlier my model size was 6.4GB and now it got reduced to 800MB, after making this change it is working.

Thanks for your support.
